Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:10.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:39.22,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Licht and his comrades finally\N completed their reincarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:42.10,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and headed to the royal capital\N to commence their attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:50.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel, Noelle, Mimosa, Zora, Kirsch, En,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.28,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and Mereoleona,\Nwho was still knocked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,left the hideout and headed \Nback toward the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.41,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like some place is \Nalready being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:00:59.65,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...Hage Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.79,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.16,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Nash! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:10.24,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno took a different route in \Norder to save their home, Hage Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:14.42,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,from an attack by a Magic Knight \Nwho'd reincarnated as an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.59,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.56,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Good job fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:19.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...Nash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:22.39,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.14,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Crescent Moon Sickle, Four Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.60,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell from his mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The elf's soul inside him is in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:36.31,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the elves are asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:37.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.50,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:42.08,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he's going to turn \Ninto something besides an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We have to set him free.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.92,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He negated... the reincarnation spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:58.74,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,With this sword... \NI'll be able to save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.72,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning of Rage vs. Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that giant \Nboulder-looking thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.34,main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.25,main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:03.30,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I guess I'll go have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.45,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The town...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.05,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's being attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.32,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading into town, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.45,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get on your own damn broom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be bashful! Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.66,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not bashful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.92,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... H-Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.17,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead, Crazy Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:50.93,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Up ahead, I feel elven magic from \Nboth the north and the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:54.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Since there are two places, it'd be \Nbetter if we split up and helped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.10,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.63,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,See you at the royal capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.50,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We came to this town because \Nit was under attack, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:29.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.62,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:38.60,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.37,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.35,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:00.69,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I think he wanted to see someone.\NWas it you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.04,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:07.55,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the reincarnation spell, \Nthis body belongs to me, Rufel, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Reincarnation? Rufel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.26,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.80,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:17.85,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It means someone else \Nhas taken over Luck's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.86,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Those Eye of the Midnight Sun guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.11,Default,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.51,Default,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Luck and the other Royal Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.21,Default,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,headed to the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:34.12,Default,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Then was that flying boulder thing their...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.58,Default,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:40.19,Default,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the plan to eliminate them failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:47.19,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! I guess you're \Nnot as dumb as you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:51.39,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, those Royal Knights \Nor whatever were completely wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.13,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, if you guys are \Nalso going to get in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.93,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,you're gonna have to die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.53,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.93,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up attacking somewhere \Ncompletely different?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:18.03,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is this a spell to protect your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.46,Default,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.04,Default,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.75,Default,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna burn you to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.87,Default,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Explosive Scatterâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.77,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The red thread of fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.72,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge is on the side of all the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:45.69,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So she'll protect Luck, even though \Nhis body is possessed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.01,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Shut down your damn cat's powers, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.44,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If Luck's attack had connected,\N you would've died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:59.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if it really is the forbidden \Nspell, Luck is just asleep, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:04.37,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm trying to \Nwake that fool back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:12.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Flame Magic: Explosive Scattershot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.91,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Such a simple spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.35,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it'll hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.60,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared? \NBut I still sense their mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.10,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I call this "Explosive \NAnnihilation Scattershot"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.82,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There's no spell that can hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:40.66,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you humans can't defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.54,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:47.63,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Do you think \Nyou can dodge my attacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.08,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.92,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, all of you people \Nare so overly enthusiastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.97,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you actually \Nmanage to defeat Luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.73,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,that might shock him enough to wake him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.73,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.07,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Explosive Scatter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:17.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Show him the results of \Nall your training with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.08,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I plan \Non doing, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.98,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Again, that spell won't hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:37.38,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is my newest Explosive Scattershot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.89,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I call it "Time Bomb Explosive Scattershot"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter if it hits you \Nor not! It'll still explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.28,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can tell which ones will explode?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Your puny little spell isn't going to hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.59,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to amuse me a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.26,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing fireballs that \Ndon't disappear {\i1}or{\i0} explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to be a feint?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.55,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you out of magic already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.26,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If he's dodging by sensing where mana is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.72,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Magna can get behind him by mixing \Nin some regular Scattershots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.72,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to hit him at this distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.81,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.52,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed your mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:40.74,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fully aware of your ability \Nto sense mana and your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:50.10,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He made sure it would explode\Nright at this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:11:01.30,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm stupid enough to \Nmake myself explode, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:15.27,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If you were actually Luck, you'd probably\N figure that I'd do something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.65,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm way more skilled than you when it comes to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.24,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,resilience and being able to take a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:25.53,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Gargantuan Exploding Fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:36.34,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And then... Flame Bondage Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:43.78,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I know Luck really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.64,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the hell you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:53.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't know a damn \Nthing about him or me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:56.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have no chance of beating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:01.11,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If that's crystal clear, then hurry up \Nand return that idiot to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:12.62,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.73,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.48,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,can't beat whom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.38,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,human?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:13:02.09,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you explain just how \Nyou humans expect to defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:08.55,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on! I'll keep throwing \Nthese at you until Luck wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.89,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:16.52,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks will never hit me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.73,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He's moving so fast, I can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:30.66,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can't keep up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:39.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He was already a monster, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:40.88,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.39,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:02.15,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The power to control... the future? \NNo, to control fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.94,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But it appears you can't attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:11.43,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I'm pretty sure that \Npower uses quite a bit of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:16.07,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The magic of elves, who are blessed \Nby mana, or the magic of you humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:19.62,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think will last longer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.95,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Tired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.03,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even broken a sweat yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.66,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That ended much more quickly than I'd hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.02,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The humans of the Clover Kingdom\N will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:30.79,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you deserve, and that's the \Nfate we elves shall bring upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.11,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Shut... up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.62,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.06,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're an elf or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.12,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to that idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:53.39,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,So you can hurry up and get the \Nhell out of that body, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:58.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's a mischievous little brat who's always \Nbeing reckless and causing us trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.31,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But Luck is my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.74,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You humans betray each \Nother at the drop of a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.15,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me \Nyou actually have a bond?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:11.81,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.27,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you can do will break \Nthis reincarnation spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:17.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Especially not your flimsy little bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:21.41,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This human's soul has already been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:29.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.55,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Acting like someone you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're still in there, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.69,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,While you were off messing around,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:47.11,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I was out training and got \Nsuper strong, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:52.20,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If that pisses you off, then get the \Nhell out here and fight me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:02.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Luck, don't you dare think you \Ncan get rid of us that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:07.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,My red thread of fate is\N never going to let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:09.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.50,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.80,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.61,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.68,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:25.44,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:36.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,going to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.20,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge used up the last of her magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:49.21,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,to bring upon the fate that \Nwould bring Asta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.95,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You know damn well who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll repeat myself as \Nmany times as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're Luck's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.69,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.02,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:15.26,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, eh? You're all \Nreally getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.32,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a lick of magic, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:23.54,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought anyone in this world\N could be so unloved by mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:27.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And the first ones to ever acknowledge \Nme and consider me one of their own
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,were the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:33.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you take a single one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who or what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:40.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be able to see my movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.60,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You can die at the hands \Nof your precious friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.19,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a human can \Nkeep up with this speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.84,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,How are you able to keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:18.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your ki is filled with rage that\Nmakes it super easy to read!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And this sword is sensitive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,to really powerful magic, \Nand will seek it wherever it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.56,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.25,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.84,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:48.54,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Like you could actually surpass my rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:59.48,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be able to detect me, \Nbut his combat sense is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:01.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! Miz Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I need you guys to back me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.26,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:12.85,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You really think these attacks \Nare going to hit me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:14.56,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.86,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out how fast you are by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.07,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.58,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My body can't hold out much longer...\N I need to make the next one count!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.31,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:40.77,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's got no magic,\Ntheir plan is just to hide him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:41.97,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.80,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spread out my mana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:48.47,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,and detect the moment your \Nsword makes my mana disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.26,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.05,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's heading straight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:56.06,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.61,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,My rage is stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.95,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:05.51,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.99,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:10.37,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.79,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,They used that thread to throw off my timing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.92,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:24.97,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Our feelings are tougher than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.35,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll free you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.15,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's still got all this power left?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:47.03,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who are going to die, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up already, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:56.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We told you! We're not \Nletting go, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.29,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:06.55,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:42.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Luck, you're my precious little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:44.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come back so you can tease Magna
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:46.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and eat other people's puddings without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:50.57,main,vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \NPage 105: "Smiles, Tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 105\N\N{\fs18} Smiles, Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:53.95,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anything sever the \Nbond that the Black Bulls have!
